{"tid":1556510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"月薪三千內地招聘港大學生","createTime":"2019-09-09T18:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T09:45:11.000Z","uid":297241,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"068a43cad99e167e38cf21e44a3f88c1948d9bba","tid":1556510,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:13:32.000Z","msg":"月薪三千內地招聘港大學生<br />\n<br />\n一間人力資源公司將會在本月底舉行招聘會，為台灣及內地企業招聘本港人才，預料會有三十多間企業提供約一千個職位空缺。該公司負責人透露，內地企業有興趣吸納本港大學畢業生，提供食住及薪俸稅津貼，但月薪只有二千至三千港元。另外，台灣的半導體企業亦有興趣招請本港電子工程系畢業生，但首年必須先到內地受訓。"},{"pid":"404b776663ee3ed75aa9af98870a8d1072c2dc16","tid":1556510,"uid":2904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[全民和你唱]</span></span> 全世界全天候街邊唱香港國歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556100</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cea1aa73849fa7c41b28c6a256cd65f7fa42491d","tid":1556510,"uid":229653,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:28:58.000Z","msg":"On9先會去做<br />\n我地d土生土長嘅香港人只做外國brand公司<br />\n港共嘅留返比啲nds la"},{"pid":"0f19a2abd39f37a13b479ff726ed48e3310cc4a3","tid":1556510,"uid":100638,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:30:55.000Z","msg":"大陸人工係咁上下<br />\n幾撚吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲低撚過做M記"},{"pid":"9c0b763f67065f00c9ec72f0ff7855dcb1a6498f","tid":1556510,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:31:38.000Z","msg":"3000 蚊不了 不過佢地北大清華都係1萬人工 應該算高"},{"pid":"641db5e4f6a9683bb3dcf807b410b18c1bb53153","tid":1556510,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:33:25.000Z","msg":"二千至三千 中六畢業都唔做啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9384609cf18729bdd98490098492eeb1f074a31","tid":1556510,"uid":14361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy